casebody.data:
Maritza MASTRAPA, Appellant,
v.
8221 STAR LLC, Appellee. No. 3D17-2591 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. Opinion filed May 9, 2018 Maritza Mastrapa, in proper person. Bill Ullman and Rosenny Burgos, for appellee. Before FERNANDEZ, SCALES and LUCK, JJ. PER CURIAM.

Affirmed. See Fla. R. App. P. 9.315(a) ("After service of the initial brief ... the court may summarily affirm the order to be reviewed if the court finds that no preliminary basis for reversal has been demonstrated.").
